1) Download and Load The Data 7

STEP 1: 

  • Click on the  red button above to download  the Zip file "Tsa Zipped".   It Contains the data that we are using to build the dashboard.

STEP 2: 

  • Open the downloaded file
  • Extract the zipped file 


STEP 3:

  • Open the Power BI Desktop. 
  • Click on get data.



  • Select Excel .



  • Browse to the location of  "TSA Dataset" Excel File and Open it.


  • Select 3 tables : Airport, Calendar, TSA Claim.
  • Click on load button.
